      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely perfect shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every single service schedule. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin!",
