    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated straight-six, complete with factory-spec individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed OEM specifications. The chassis remains perfectly balanced with a 50/50 weight distribution, supported by pristine bushings and a mechanical limited-slip differential that provides immediate lock-up under load. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its original factory clear coat with zero oxidation. This is a collector-tier specimen with a fully documented service history, ready for the most discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
