      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most meticulous inspection. This car has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the factory paint retains its deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the supple leather upholstery remains firm and unmarked, all interior electronics operate with tactile precision, and the original scent remains. Mechanically, the car is flawless, delivering a drive that is as tight and responsive as the day it was assembled. It comes accompanied by a comprehensive binder of all service records, confirming a history of preventative maintenance and zero compromises. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks, feels, and performs as if it just rolled off the delivery truck.",
