      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example featuring the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. This chassis has been meticulously preserved with proactive rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, and structural subframe reinforcement already completed. The suspension geometry remains true with zero bushing compliance issues, and the undercarriage is free of oxidative stress. A turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical harmony.",
